Package: buddydrive
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsodium23, libsqlite3-0, libgtk-4-1
Description: P2P encrypted folder sync with buddies
 BuddyDrive is a peer-to-peer encrypted folder synchronization tool.
 It allows syncing folders with 1-2 friends across the internet,
 bypassing NATs and firewalls using libp2p.
 .
 Features:
  - P2P networking with DHT discovery
  - End-to-end encryption using libsodium
  - SQLite-based file index
  - systemd service support
  - GTK4 graphical interface
